branchCategory.description:
&lt;p&gt;
Direct air operated, 2 port valve series VXA can be used with a wide variety of fluids. Two body materials are offered: brass (C37) and stainless steel. Pilot port size is 1/8 inch. Flow rate ranges from Cv of 0.38 to 2.8.
&lt;/p&gt;

